        "content": "<p>heiher opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13675\">PR #13675</a> from <code>heiher:fiber-loong64</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Add LoongArch64 fiber support for Wasmtime.</p>\n<p>This fixes the runtime error:</p>\n<p><code>fibers not supported on this host architecture</code></p>\n<p>by implementing the required stack switching and unwind support for LoongArch64.</p>\n<p>Procedure Call Standard for the LoongArch™ Architecture: <a href=\"https://github.com/loongson/la-abi-specs/blob/release/lapcs.adoc#processor-architecture\">https://github.com/loongson/la-abi-specs/blob/release/lapcs.adoc#processor-architecture</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
